{"tid":1742144,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[新戰法]塞佢老母低成本新招，可避免比人打同增加阻礙時間！","createTime":"2019-11-20T15:53:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-08T13:55:00.000Z","uid":92479,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"315df9d6d61715c8c9010ec38815450c2d56a14b","tid":1742144,"uid":92479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T15:53:59.000Z","msg":"好驚有人咁做<br />\n快速倒大陸果款痴地毯既萬能膠(又臭又痴)落地下<br />\n可以用膠樽入左先 ( 蓋頂開幾個窿可以唧出黎)<br />\n跟住放多塊老鼠膠板係面<br />\n個撚個都唔敢上車落車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n千祁唔好放係幕門上幕門前<br />\n一陣啲膠痴撚晒落幕門到，開關會愈黎愈有問題<br />\n退一萬步係站外出入口都可能會發生，千祁唔好鋪到跳都跳唔過<br />\n窄路所需物料更少<br />\n註*可配合其他物料<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最緊要HIT &amp; RUN 減少比藍屍同狗搞既機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d71c3dbef7a2162b85467ea98bd12c77cf22bf2","tid":1742144,"uid":92479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T15:54:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"604a41eb2dfc3500b2401de5f801cfeb7fe7263a","tid":1742144,"uid":326463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T15:54:21.000Z","msg":"借過位<br />\n[多圖]11.21 曙光行動2.0，721 4.0<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1741920\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1741920</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e2a39a1299c0f2ff43f03595691cb362646991e7","tid":1742144,"uid":92479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T15:54:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/9070511611/640\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.gtimg.com%2Fnewsapp_bt%2F0%2F9070511611%2F640&h=775b1e43&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0691ce7bf92006c93d60297ecfe962527c95e0a3","tid":1742144,"uid":92479,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T15:55:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcT7yNHG